### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

### 当前租户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tenants/current
X-Tenant-Id: default

### 路线图层
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gis/road-routes?routeCode=G210
X-Tenant-Id: default

### 路段图层
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gis/road-sections?routeCode=G210
X-Tenant-Id: default

### 评定单元图层
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gis/evaluation-units?routeCode=G210
X-Tenant-Id: default

### 病害图层
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gis/diseases?routeCode=G210
X-Tenant-Id: default

### 评定专题图层
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gis/assessment-results?routeCode=G210&year=2026&indexCode=MQI
X-Tenant-Id: default

### 病害热点分析
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/analyze/disease
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: default

{
  "routeCode": "G210",
  "year": 2026
}

### 路线综合分析
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/analyze/route
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: default

{
  "routeCode": "G210",
  "year": 2026
}

### 评定结果分析
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/analyze/assessment
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: default

{
  "routeCode": "G210",
  "year": 2026,
  "indexCode": "PCI"
}

### 地图联动查询
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/map-query
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: default

{
  "message": "把 PCI 较低的次差路段显示出来",
  "routeCode": "G210",
  "year": 2026,
  "grade": "POOR",
  "indexCode": "PCI"
}

### 评定报告草稿
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/report/assessment
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: default

{
  "routeCode": "G210",
  "year": 2026
}

### AI 问答
POST http://localhost:8080/api/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: default

{
  "message": "分析 G210 2026 年整体路况，并指出重点养护路段",
  "context": {
    "routeCode": "G210",
    "year": 2026,
    "indexCode": "MQI"
  }
}
